name: 西斯·金

last_movies.title: 杰西卡·琼斯 第二季

introduction: Cece King is an actor, writer, producer. She grew up in New Jersey and moved to Los Angeles when she was nineteen where she attended New York Film Academy.King has since made television appearances in Showtime's "Masters of Sex", CBS All Access "All My Children", CBS "The Good Fight" and most recently Marvel's "Jessica Jones". Also appearing in independent films "All Square" alongside Josh Lucas and Michael Kelly (House of Cards) which won the SXSW narrative film award. "Through The Glass Darkly" which premiered opening night (2020) at Frameline Film Festival opposite Shanola Hampton (Shameless) and Robyn Lively (Teen Witch). "The Broken Ones" opposite Constance Shulman (Orange Is The New Black) and Margaret Colin (Gossip Girl, Independence Day) distributed by Multicom Entertainment.As a writer she is in development on her next feature film "Dear Jack", which was adapted from a book. Variety has announced Annette Haywood-Carter to direct.
